    "department": "Technology",
    "description": "Purpose in Every Position\n\nPebl puts a world of talent at your fingertips. With our AI-powered Global Work Platform™, companies can hire, pay, and manage employees in 185+ countries—removing risk, red tape, and guesswork from global growth. Backed by more than a decade of compliance leadership and local expertise, Pebl helps businesses move fast, stay compliant, and scale with confidence. With Pebl, companies everywhere can hire great talent anywhere.\n\nWhere Your Work Moves the Needle.\n\nAt Pebl, every team member drives our success. Joining us means more than filling a role—you’re accountable for results and impact. Our values guide how we operate, execute, and collaborate across borders. By putting them into action, you’ll help us scale faster, compete harder, and lead the future of global work.\n\nAbout Pebl\nWith Pebl, companies everywhere can hire great talent anywhere.\nWe’re building the infrastructure that makes global hiring seamless—unlocking access to opportunity for individuals and helping companies build the best teams without borders.\n\nWe’re early, moving quickly, and intentional about building a high-caliber team. While we may not have a role that perfectly matches your background today, we’re always looking to connect with exceptional engineers, product leaders, and designers in Palo Alto.\n\nWho We’re Looking For\nWe’re interested in connecting with:\n\n - Software Engineers (Backend, Frontend, Full Stack, Infrastructure)\n\n - Product Managers (Core Product, Growth, Platform)\n\n - Designers (Product Design, UX/UI, Design Systems)\n\n - Engineering \u0026 Product Leaders (Tech Leads, Managers, Directors)\n\nYou might be a great fit if you:\n\n - Care deeply about building thoughtful, high-quality products end-to-end\n\n - Enjoy turning ambiguity into clear, usable solutions\n\n - Move quickly and know how to prioritize in fast-changing environments\n\n - Take ownership and think in terms of outcomes, not just output\n\n - Are based in or open to Palo Alto\n\nWhat You Might Work On\nAs we scale Pebl, areas of focus may include:\n\n - Building the core infrastructure powering global hiring\n\n - Designing seamless, intuitive experiences for companies and candidates\n\n - Creating scalable design systems and improving UX across the platform\n\n - Driving product strategy and shipping high-impact features\n\n - Leveraging modern technologies, including AI, to improve hiring efficiency\n\nWhy Pebl\n\n - Meaningful, real-world impact on how people work globally\n\n - Small, high-talent team with a strong bias for action\n\n - Significant ownership across engineering, product, and design\n\n - Competitive compensation and equity\n\n - Opportunity to shape both the product and the user experience from an early stage\n\nWhat This Is (and Isn’t)\nThis isn’t a role tied to an immediate opening—it’s a way for us to build relationships early with people we’re excited about.\n\nIf there’s alignment, we may reach out for an introductory conversation. Otherwise, we’ll keep you in mind as new roles open.\n\nLet’s Stay Connected\nIf you’re exploring what’s next—or expect to be soon—we’d love to get to know you.\n\nOur Commitment to You\n\nAt Pebl, we’re committed to supporting our team with comprehensive rewards and benefits designed to meet diverse needs across roles and locations. Our core offerings include:\n\n - Flexible Time Off – Take the time you need to recharge.\n\n - Parental Leave – Support for growing families.\n\n - Health and Dental Insurance – Where applicable, to cover you and your loved ones.\n\n - Retirement Savings + Employee Incentive Plan – Plan for the future while sharing our success.\n\nPlease visit our career page for more information https://hellopebl.com/company/careers/.\n\nPebl is an Equal Opportunity Employer.\n\nWe power global teams and believe diverse perspectives drive innovation and impact. Employment decisions at Pebl are based on qualifications, merit, and business needs. We do not discriminate on the basis of race, color, religion, sex (including pregnancy, sexual orientation, or gender identity), national origin, age, disability, genetic information, veteran status, or any other status protected by applicable law. We’re committed to fostering an inclusive culture where every teammate can thrive and do the best work of their career—anywhere in the world.",
    "employment_type": "FullTime",
